1SAPPLY* is the state machine analog of 1APPLY*.  This procedure checks out
what kind of procedure is to be applied.  If it is primitive, the appropriate
magic occurs.  If it is a procedural closure, we evaluate the body of the
closed procedure in an environment constructed by binding the formal parameters
of the closed procedure to the actual parameters (in 1ARGS*) in the environment
carried in the closure.
